 Mụ tự hoà thượng” - 覆和潘茂才贈天姥寺和尚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%C6%A1-ng%C5%A9-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tr%E1%BB%B1c-%C4%91oan-ng%E1%BB%8D-ti%E1%BA%BFt-t%E1%BB%83-sinh-vi-l%E1%BB%85-nh%C3%A2n-th%C3%A0nh-tam-lu%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-QiGWBcDEaqdKm-B9fPWuSQ">Sơ ngũ nhật trực đoan ngọ tiết tể sinh vi lễ nhân thành tam luật kỳ 2 - 初五日直端午節宰牲為禮，因成三律其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%A1t-Li%E1%BB%85u/poem-xdpmxMrS5eWC5GOr-k4MCg">Tần Cát Liễu - 秦吉了</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%E1%BB%A8c-%E1%BA%A5u-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-gL1ae9_rOBLfvJazfocz3g">Ức ấu tử - 憶幼子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Quan-%C3%82m-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-f76aMK64Up98A9l81s92VQ">Vọng Quan Âm miếu - 望觀音廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
